---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="For Pharma Marketing Services · Compleo Advisors" description={"For pharma marketing services companies driving growth and market leadership. Defensible positioning, deliberate market presence, and the new business engine that turns deep expertise into sustained growth."} slug="for-pharma-marketing-services" pathname="/for-pharma-marketing-services" active="for-pharma-marketing-services">

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner reveal">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">For Pharma Marketing Services</div>
      <h1>For pharma marketing services companies driving <span class="accent">growth and market leadership</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Defensible positioning, deliberate market presence, and the new business engine that turns deep expertise into sustained growth.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="scenarios">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="scenarios-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">Where we step in</p>
      <h2>The moments we step into.</h2>
      <p>Four common scenarios where marketing services firms bring us in.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="scenario-grid">
      <article class="scenario-card reveal">
        <div class="scenario-number">Scenario 01</div>
        <h3>Standing out in a crowded category.</h3>
        <p>The capabilities are real and the work is strong, and yet the market sees the firm as one of many. Compleo Advisors defines the positioning that captures what actually differentiates the business and translates it into a story the market can recognize.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="scenario-card reveal">
        <div class="scenario-number">Scenario 02</div>
        <h3>Reaching the right buyers.</h3>
        <p>Pharma decision-makers are hard to access and slow to switch. Compleo Advisors builds the go-to-market approach that reaches the right people through the right channels with content that earns their attention.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="scenario-card reveal">
        <div class="scenario-number">Scenario 03</div>
        <h3>Winning the right engagements.</h3>
        <p>Growth depends on winning the engagements that fit, not the most engagements. Compleo Advisors helps define the ideal client profile, sharpen the qualification approach, and shape the new business strategy that draws fit-for-purpose work.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="scenario-card reveal">
        <div class="scenario-number">Scenario 04</div>
        <h3>Building market presence and thought leadership.</h3>
        <p>Senior leaders have perspective and the market needs to see it. Compleo Advisors designs the thought leadership platform, content strategy, and presence-building work that establish the firm as a category voice.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="changes">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="changes-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">The outcome</p>
      <h2>What changes.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="changes-list">
      <div class="changes-item reveal">
        <h3>Positioning becomes ownable.</h3>
        <p>The story stops sounding like every other firm in the category. Differentiation becomes specific and defensible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="changes-item reveal">
        <h3>Market presence becomes deliberate.</h3>
        <p>Thought leadership, content, and visibility are designed around a position the firm actually owns, with cadence and channel choices that compound over time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="changes-item reveal">
        <h3>Growth becomes selective.</h3>
        <p>The pipeline shifts toward better-fit engagements, and the conversations that come in match the work the firm wants to do.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="services-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">Services</p>
      <h2>What we do for marketing services firms.</h2>
      <p>Strategy and execution that move together, sequenced to where you are.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="services-col reveal">
        <h4>Strategic services</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Positioning and category definition</li>
          <li>Competitive analysis and market mapping</li>
          <li>Ideal client profile and qualification framework</li>
          <li>Go-to-market strategy and channel design</li>
          <li>Thought leadership platform and content strategy</li>
          <li>New business strategy and pipeline development</li>
          <li>Custom strategic engagements based on your need</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="services-col reveal">
        <h4>Tactical and creative services</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Brand identity and verbal identity development</li>
          <li>Content and editorial program design</li>
          <li>Website and digital ecosystem strategy</li>
          <li>Executive thought leadership development</li>
          <li>Speaker, event, and PR strategy</li>
          <li>Sales enablement materials and pitch design</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="proof">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="proof-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">Proof</p>
      <h2>The work, in practice.</h2>
      <p>A featured engagement from inside a marketing services firm.</p>
    </div>

    <article class="proof-card reveal" style="max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 44px;">
      <div class="case-label">Featured Case · Thought Leadership Transformation</div>
      <h3 style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:18px;">From deep talent to a category voice.</h3>
      <p>A professional services firm with deep internal expertise had no visibility in its field online. Compleo Advisors transformed that internal expertise into a compelling, cyclical thought leadership program, leveraged through highly targeted media to drive and convert leads.</p>
      <p>The program built a defensible market position and reshaped how the firm was discovered and chosen by fit-for-purpose buyers. Results were measurable and durable.</p>
      <p class="case-status">Full case study available on request.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="closing reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Sharpening your position in the market? Let's talk.</h2>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a conversation <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      <a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary">See how we work <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</SiteLayout>

<style is:global>
/* COMPLEO ADVISORS — FOR PHARMA MARKETING SERVICES MOCKUP v1 (audience-page template) */

/* tokens in global.css */

*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{margin:0;font-family:var(--font-stack);font-size:var(--fs-body);line-height:var(--lh-body);color:var(--c-body);background:var(--c-white);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;text-rendering:optimizeLegibility;}
img,svg{display:block;max-width:100%;}
a{color:var(--c-charcoal);text-decoration:none;transition:color .15s ease;}
a:hover{color:var(--c-amber);}

h1,h2,h3,h4{font-family:var(--font-stack);color:var(--c-near-black);margin:0;line-height:var(--lh-tight);letter-spacing:-0.01em;}
h1{font-size:var(--fs-h1-desktop);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.02em;}
h2{font-size:var(--fs-h2-desktop);font-weight:600;}
h3{font-size:var(--fs-h3-desktop);font-weight:500;line-height:var(--lh-snug);}
p{margin:0 0 1em;}
p:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}

.container{width:100%;max-width:var(--content-max);margin:0 auto;padding:0 var(--gutter);}
.container-narrow{width:100%;max-width:var(--content-narrow);margin:0 auto;padding:0 var(--gutter);}
.container-reading{width:100%;max-width:var(--content-reading);margin:0 auto;padding:0 var(--gutter);}
section{padding:var(--section-y-desktop) 0;}

.eyebrow{font-size:var(--fs-small);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--c-amber);margin:0 0 16px;}

.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:14px 26px;font-family:var(--font-stack);font-size:16px;font-weight:500;border-radius:var(--radius);border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:background .18s ease,color .18s ease,border-color .18s ease,transform .18s ease;}
.btn-primary{background:var(--c-amber);color:var(--c-white);}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--c-charcoal);color:var(--c-white);}
.btn-secondary{background:transparent;color:var(--c-charcoal);border:1.5px solid var(--c-rule-gray);}
.btn-secondary:hover{border-color:var(--c-charcoal);color:var(--c-near-black);}
.btn .arrow{display:inline-block;transition:transform .18s ease;}
.btn:hover .arrow{transform:translateX(4px);}

.arrow-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-weight:500;color:var(--c-charcoal);}
.arrow-link::after{content:"→";transition:transform .18s ease;}
.arrow-link:hover{color:var(--c-amber);}
.arrow-link:hover::after{transform:translateX(4px);}

/* HEADER */
.site-header{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.96);backdrop-filter:saturate(180%) blur(10px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:saturate(180%) blur(10px);border-bottom:var(--rule);}
.nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:18px 0;}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;color:var(--c-near-black);}
.brand-mark{width:36px;height:36px;}
.brand-words{display:flex;flex-direction:column;line-height:1;}
.brand-name{font-weight:600;font-size:18px;color:var(--c-charcoal);letter-spacing:-0.005em;}
.nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:28px;list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;}
.nav-links a{font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--c-charcoal);}
.nav-links a.active{color:var(--c-amber);}
.nav-cta{margin-left:10px;padding:10px 20px;background:var(--c-amber);color:var(--c-white)!important;border-radius:var(--radius);font-weight:500;}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--c-charcoal);color:var(--c-white)!important;}
.nav-toggle{display:none;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;color:var(--c-charcoal);font-size:22px;padding:8px;}

/* HERO (audience-specific, wide editorial) */
.hero{position:relative;padding:84px 0 72px;overflow:hidden;}
.hero-inner{max-width:1080px;}
.hero-eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--c-mid-gray);margin-bottom:32px;}
.hero-eyebrow::before{content:"";display:inline-block;width:48px;height:2px;background:var(--c-amber);}
.hero h1{font-size:clamp(40px,6.2vw,76px);line-height:1.06;font-weight:600;color:var(--c-near-black);margin-bottom:28px;max-width:22ch;letter-spacing:-0.02em;}
.hero h1 .accent{color:var(--c-amber);background-image:linear-gradient(var(--c-amber),var(--c-amber));background-size:100% 6px;background-position:0 96%;background-repeat:no-repeat;padding-bottom:2px;}
.hero-sub{font-size:clamp(19px,2vw,22px);line-height:1.5;color:var(--c-charcoal);max-width:62ch;font-weight:400;}

/* SCENARIOS 2x2 */
.scenarios{background:var(--c-light-gray);}
.scenarios-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:36px;}
.scenarios-header h2{margin-bottom:12px;}
.scenarios-header p{color:var(--c-mid-gray);font-size:17px;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;}
.scenario-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:20px;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;}
.scenario-card{background:var(--c-white);border:1px solid var(--c-rule-gray);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:32px 30px;transition:border-color .2s ease,transform .2s ease,box-shadow .2s ease;}
.scenario-card:hover{border-color:var(--c-amber);transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 14px 32px -16px rgba(74,74,74,0.18);}
.scenario-number{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--c-amber);margin-bottom:12px;}
.scenario-card h3{font-size:21px;font-weight:600;color:var(--c-near-black);margin-bottom:14px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.3;}
.scenario-card p{font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--c-charcoal);}

/* WHAT CHANGES */
.changes{padding-top:var(--section-y-desktop);padding-bottom:var(--section-y-desktop);}
.changes-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:36px;}
.changes-list{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;}
.changes-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:240px 1fr;gap:40px;align-items:start;}
.changes-item h3{font-size:21px;font-weight:600;color:var(--c-near-black);line-height:1.25;padding-top:4px;border-left:3px solid var(--c-amber);padding-left:18px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;}
.changes-item p{font-size:17px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--c-charcoal);}

/* SERVICES TWO-COL */
.services{background:var(--c-warm-cream);}
.services-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px;}
.services-header h2{margin-bottom:12px;}
.services-header p{color:var(--c-charcoal);font-size:17px;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;}
.services-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;}
.services-col h4{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--c-amber);margin-bottom:20px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--c-amber);}
.services-col ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;}
.services-col li{padding:11px 0 11px 22px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--c-charcoal);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(74,74,74,0.12);position:relative;}
.services-col li::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:0;top:18px;width:10px;height:2px;background:var(--c-amber);}
.services-col li:last-child{border-bottom:none;}

/* PROOF */
.proof{padding-top:var(--section-y-desktop);padding-bottom:var(--section-y-desktop);}
.proof-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px;}
.proof-header h2{margin-bottom:12px;}
.proof-header p{color:var(--c-mid-gray);font-size:17px;max-width:580px;margin:0 auto;}
.proof-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;}
.proof-card{background:var(--c-white);border:1px solid var(--c-rule-gray);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:32px 30px;position:relative;}
.proof-card .case-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--c-amber);margin-bottom:14px;}
.proof-card h3{font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:var(--c-near-black);margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.3;letter-spacing:-0.01em;}
.proof-card p{font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--c-charcoal);}
.proof-card .case-status{margin-top:16px;font-size:12px;color:var(--c-mid-gray);font-style:italic;}

/* CLOSING CTA */
.closing{background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--c-warm-cream) 0%,var(--c-warm-cream-2) 100%);text-align:center;padding:60px 0;}
.closing h2{font-size:clamp(28px,3.4vw,40px);font-weight:600;color:var(--c-near-black);margin:0 auto 24px;max-width:24ch;line-height:1.25;}
.closing .cta-row{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;}

/* FOOTER */
.site-footer{background:var(--c-near-black);color:#B3B3B3;padding:64px 0 32px;font-size:14px;}
.footer-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr 1fr;gap:48px;margin-bottom:48px;}
.footer-brand .brand-name{color:var(--c-white);}
.footer-tag{margin-top:16px;color:#B3B3B3;max-width:32ch;line-height:1.5;}
.footer-col h4{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--c-amber);margin-bottom:16px;}
.footer-col ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;}
.footer-col li{margin-bottom:10px;}
.footer-col a{color:#B3B3B3;}
.footer-col a:hover{color:var(--c-white);}
.footer-bottom{border-top:1px solid #444;padding-top:24px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-size:13px;color:#777;}

/* REVEAL */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease;}
.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none;}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media (max-width:960px){
  :root{--section-y-desktop:var(--section-y-mobile);}
  body{font-size:var(--fs-body-mobile);}
  h1{font-size:var(--fs-h1-mobile);}
  h2{font-size:var(--fs-h2-mobile);}
  h3{font-size:var(--fs-h3-mobile);}
  .nav-links{display:none;}
  .nav-toggle{display:block;}
  .nav.open .nav-links{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:18px;position:absolute;top:100%;left:0;right:0;background:var(--c-white);padding:24px var(--gutter);border-bottom:var(--rule);}
  .hero{padding:64px 0 56px;}
  .hero h1{font-size:38px;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:20px;}
  .hero-sub{font-size:18px;}
  .hero-eyebrow{margin-bottom:24px;}
  .scenario-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:14px;}
  .scenario-card{padding:26px 22px;}
  .changes-list{gap:24px;}
  .changes-item{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:10px;}
  .services-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:32px;}
  .proof-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:14px;}
  .footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:32px;}
  .footer-bottom{flex-direction:column;gap:12px;text-align:center;}
}

/* ─── Accessibility & Print ─── */
.skip-link{position:absolute;top:-40px;left:0;background:var(--c-amber);color:var(--c-white);padding:10px 18px;z-index:200;text-decoration:none;border-radius:0 0 var(--radius) 0;font-weight:500;}
.skip-link:focus{top:0;color:var(--c-white);outline:none;}
:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--c-amber);outline-offset:3px;border-radius:3px;}
button:focus-visible,a:focus-visible,input:focus-visible,select:focus-visible,textarea:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--c-amber);outline-offset:3px;}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
  html{scroll-behavior:auto;}
  *,*::before,*::after{transition-duration:0.001ms!important;animation-duration:0.001ms!important;animation-iteration-count:1!important;}
  .reveal{opacity:1!important;transform:none!important;}
}

@media print{
  *{background:transparent!important;color:#000!important;box-shadow:none!important;text-shadow:none!important;}
  .site-header,.site-footer,.nav-toggle,.nav-cta,.cta-row,.btn,.hero-eyebrow::before,.amber-rule,.signup,.closing,.next,.form-section,#navToggle,.nav-links{display:none!important;}
  body{font-size:11pt;line-height:1.45;background:#fff!important;}
  h1{font-size:24pt;}
  h2{font-size:18pt;}
  h3{font-size:14pt;}
  .container,.container-narrow,.container-reading,.hero-inner{max-width:100%!important;padding:0!important;}
  section{padding:18pt 0!important;page-break-inside:avoid;}
  a{color:#000!important;text-decoration:underline;}
  a[href^="http"]:after{content:" ("attr(href)")";font-size:9pt;color:#555;}
  .reveal{opacity:1!important;transform:none!important;}
  .hero h1 .accent{background:none!important;padding-bottom:0!important;}
}
</style>
